{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act39side", "eventName": "出蒼白海", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EP-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "重逢不乏意外", "storyInfo": "營地中船員們因為物資匱乏而人心惶惶，哈維爾想要帶領船員歸順小鎮。安納斯塔西奧也對雅隆鎮生出了一些不該有的想法。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g12_alchemyworkshop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "手臂和腿都還在，臉也沒有破相，就是變黑了一點……", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是太好了！你不知道我聽說他們這些強盜冷血無情、殺人如麻的時候，我有多緊張！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這些話都是從哪裡聽來的……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是付出了多大的勇氣才敢跑到這裡來救你的啊！溫蒂還留在小鎮裡，我現在就傳……", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）等你準備好了，我再傳訊息給她，然後想辦法離開這裡！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我試過了，逃不出去的，而且，短期內我不打算離開。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#6$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？難道你真如傳言一般加入了強盜的船隊？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#5$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）老實告訴我，你真覺得在這個窮鄉僻壤當強盜很有前途嗎？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我對當海盜不感興趣，極境。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#10$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我留下是因為……我想重拾當年自己逃避掉的煉金研究。這可是搭載了心相原質的羅盤啊……這個世界上可能就只剩下這一枚了。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且……我答應他們要修好羅盤了。沒有羅盤，他們很難繼續活下去。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……你以後也打算一直跟他們走？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，等到羅盤修好，這些海盜就會離開鹽漠，駛向大海。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會留下來，繼續在伊比利亞精進自己的劍術與煉金技藝。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_slapcloth_light"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "極境拍了拍伊西多的肩膀，感覺自己的朋友似乎變了一些。"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來這段日子你有很多感觸啊……也好。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，外面那個小丫頭叫我過來本來是要幹嘛的？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我修復羅盤的過程中，需要有人幫忙做些輔助操作。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#6$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那簡單，就和在羅德島一樣，有什麼需要幫忙的就和我說。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會叫你。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多走到塑金台前站定，他手中施術用的探針在空氣中劃出銳響，精密的法術能量場沿著探針的軌跡逐漸成型。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他小心翼翼地拆下羅盤的外殼，將它送上塑金台。慢慢地，羅盤內原本凝固的流體物質，也開始隨著法術能量流動的方向漾起波瀾。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "法術能量與心相原質交相輝映，淡金色的光透過工坊的縫隙，照亮了船外的鹽地。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船員們沒見過這樣的景象，一個接著一個被吸引而來。"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們在搞什麼東西？", "name": "門外的船員"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是那個外面來的小子在搞什麼煉什麼術……這道金光還蠻有趣的。", "name": "好奇的船員"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我看看讓我看看……", "name": "探頭的船員"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的還蠻酷的，你手裡的東西是什麼？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g14_ibtown_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看，那個孩子手裡的是什麼？", "name": "好奇的路人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還能有什麼，又一個小鬼為了討飯耍的把戲吧。", "name": "不屑的路人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那算了，快點走吧，我們已經沒有多餘的糧食了。", "name": "好奇的路人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "惹人煩的小鬼……", "name": "不屑的路人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戲法表演！只要一塊餅就能觀賞，諸位請不要錯——", "name": "小伊西多"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_178", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚……", "name": "小伊西多"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別擋在路中間，滾到旁邊去。", "name": "冷漠的路人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）呸，混蛋……", "name": "小伊西多"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g12_alchemyworkshop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，外面圍了好多人，會打擾你嗎？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去把他們趕走？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，有你在這裡囉嗦，感覺就像是回到之前在羅德島的工作環境。他們打擾不到我的。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#6$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多沒有停下自己的動作，手中的探針彷彿在與能量場中蕩漾的心相原質舞蹈。"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "光芒自他的掌心誕生，在窗外的船員們眼中，像是一場在乾渴與飢餓中突然出現的白日夢境。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看過這種東西嗎？這個小子還蠻厲害的啊。", "name": "門外的船員"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很久之前好像首領講過差不多的故事，說大的城鎮裡有變戲法的，看起來就是這樣。", "name": "好奇的船員"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好看……", "name": "探頭的船員"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們想看就讓他們看吧，只要別突然衝進來要把我綁了送出去換吃的就行。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……確實是他們能做出來的事。唉，人怎麼可以這樣呢？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……大家都沒有吃的就會這樣。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#6$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g14_ibtown_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哥哥……", "name": "害羞的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有吃的嗎？", "name": "小伊西多"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒……沒有，我把我的絲帶給你好嗎？", "name": "害羞的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行，你得拿吃的來換。", "name": "小伊西多"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我自己也沒有吃的……我……", "name": "害羞的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這裡有幾塊餅乾，表演一次給這位小妹妹看吧。", "name": "好心的路人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "餅乾？好吧，既然您要求了，當然可以。", "name": "小伊西多"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "57_i02", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在小伊西多的掌心，金屬開始流淌，在黑暗中變幻著色彩。"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "街邊的路人不由自主地湊了上來，他們嘴上嫌棄地罵著，但眼睛卻不曾離開少年手中的流光。"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太久了，這條破敗的街道上太久沒有出現過這樣光亮的事物了。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真美啊，我可以靠近一點看嗎？", "name": "害羞的孩子"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨便你。", "name": "小伊西多"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少年手指揮動，流淌的金屬化為一隻羽獸飛向高空，轉眼間又化為一尾鱗躍回掌心，化為鼷獸，化為馱獸……"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "映著流光的金屬馱獸在人群中肆意奔跑，留下仿若星光的碎屑在空中飄散。"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇！", "name": "好奇的路人"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過是……", "name": "不屑的路人"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給我閉嘴，好好看著吧。", "name": "好奇的路人"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上一次看到煙火是什麼時候……", "name": "冷漠的路人"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像……已經很久很久了……", "name": "冷漠的路人"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煙火？什麼是煙火？", "name": "害羞的孩子"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "圍觀的孩子鼓足了勇氣伸出手來，接住一粒飄落的星光，自指尖傳來的溫暖讓她不禁顫抖。"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是厲害的小傢伙，你讓這裡的人難得地露出了笑容。", "name": "好心的路人"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是為一口吃的罷了。", "name": "小伊西多"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……是嗎？", "name": "好心的路人"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你自己又為何而展露笑容呢，孩子？", "name": "好心的路人"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g12_alchemyworkshop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "探針牽引著心相原質，讓它流淌作一條星河，在空氣中蜿蜒。"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船員們越聚越多，窗戶上擠滿了大大小小的臉。那些因飢渴勞累而灰敗的臉，此刻都因伊西多手中的光芒而有了色彩。"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兄弟，你是故意這麼表演的吧。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別以為我看不出來！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#8$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才只是檢驗一下煉金設施和羅盤的狀態，現在才該正式從心相原質裡分離出那些鏽蝕變質了的成分。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我答應他們的……我能做到的。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g6_olddeck_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$comedy_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.5, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，你們怎麼聊了這麼久？", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#8$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這麼久沒見面，當然有很多話要聊啊，老闆，你不會一直坐在這裡等我吧？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叫什麼老闆，太客氣了，叫我小毛毛吧，我的朋友都這麼叫我。", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#7$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在又要和我以朋友相稱嗎？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對啊，要不是我這個朋友盡心幫你，你怎麼找得到自己的老朋友嘛。", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#7$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#12$1", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.0, "scale": 1.1, "duration": 0.0, "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "200,-30", "posto": "280,-30", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.7, "duration": 0.7, "focus": "l", "end": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（你這個丫頭還真會顛倒黑白。）", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "280,-30", "posto": "200,-30", "afrom": 0.7, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.7, "focus": "l", "end": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我想想啊……身為朋友，你叫我什麼比較好呢？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叫什麼都只是小事，你想要我怎麼叫都可以！重要的是，那位伊西多大人怎麼說？", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他願不願意幫幫忙，罩我一下？", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，聊得太晚，忘記了。不過你要是嘴甜一點，說不定我明天就能想起來了。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "求求你了，尊敬的小紅毛大人！超級厲害的黎博利！以及世上最最最帥的大帥哥！", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不錯，愛聽，多講幾句！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#13$1", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.0, "scale": 1.1, "duration": 0.0, "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "-200,-30", "posto": "-280,-30", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.7, "duration": 0.7, "focus": "l", "end": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（啊，可惡，你個傻鳥！）", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（敢這麼威脅我，遲早拔掉你那撮紅毛！）", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "-280,-30", "posto": "-200,-30", "afrom": 0.7, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.7, "focus": "l", "end": "true"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，算了。看在你帶著我找到了我的朋友……", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "極境伸手拍了拍眼前這個個子小小，說話和做事卻十分老成，甚至堪稱狠毒的小丫頭。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你年紀這麼小，就要在這強盜窩裡打拚，要是真的有什麼解決不了的大事，就來找我吧。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的心地是真的很不錯的哦！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 1.5, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……欸？", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#14$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……欸？？", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#14$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#15$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呸，我才不相信你！在這裡說什麼大話！", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#15$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要做什麼，還是得靠我自己！", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#15$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibbar", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再給我一塊，謝謝。", "name": "飢餓的船員"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "習武教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那種餅……唔……再、再來一盤！", "name": "飢餓的船員"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）他們這輩子是沒吃過飯嗎？", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#3$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）您不覺得很熟悉嗎？這副飛揚跋扈地索取的模樣。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#9$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）這與他們當初劫掠您的糧倉時，有任何不同嗎？", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#8$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）我不需要他們有什麼改變。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳……雖然我相信諸位已經來過雅隆鎮許多次了，以一種並不那麼和睦的方式……", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我還是歡迎你們的到來，並且對接下來要談的事務滿懷期待。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃嗝——", "name": "滿足的船員"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（舉起手臂）", "name": "滿足的船員"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是需要手帕嗎？", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用了，我有袖子。", "name": "滿足的船員"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……也好。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）呃……誰做的蒜油餅……", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）您甚至真的相信，您自己能接受他們嗎？", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#9$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）如果這樣能為小鎮帶來好處的話。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然諸位已經吃飽，我們也該談談——", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你再去給我們拿一點餅過來，我要帶回去。", "name": "滿足的船員"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用餐時間已經結束了，現在應該——", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#3$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後面那位先生，別再躲了，過來，我們好好談談。", "name": "滿足的船員"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……？", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#9$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要和你談，這個地方你說了才算，我都清楚。", "name": "滿足的船員"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……談判是證裁官的職責。你們應該找西爾弗閣下。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#8$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#3$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g11_meetingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在這裡等了我多久，小哈？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從早上就在了。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂奇沒有和你說嗎？我有些私事要去辦。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在您身邊，我從沒見您為私事苦惱。我以為……船隊的事早就佔滿了您的生活。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#7$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰說不是呢？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來找我是為了？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果……我們不用出海也能有其他出路的話，您願意放棄羅盤嗎？", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#5$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你打算怎麼做？先說說看。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#9$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些從雅隆逃回來的人說，如果我們交出羅盤與竊賊，就能得到赦免，可以在小鎮定居，想去別的地方他們也不會阻攔。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你相信了？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#9$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我核實了。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼時候？我怎麼不知道？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您還在養傷，我不想打擾您。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#2$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你不必這樣為我著想的。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#9$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您養育我長大，是我應該的。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一轉眼，你的個子都比我高了。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小時候我總在祈禱，祈禱自己能快點長大，長高一點，強壯一點，這樣就能為胡安娜女士分擔更多煩惱。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在看來，也算如願了。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#2$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論你長多大，在我心裡都還是個孩子。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#11$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我的想法呢？是否在您眼中，那依然是一個孩子的想法？", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#9$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#9$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，小哈，那並不是孩子的想法，是成人的軟弱妥協。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#9$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我寧可死都不願向他們投降……", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#9$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小哈，那些和你一起長大的夥伴，死在他們手中的又有多少？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#2$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我忘不了，胡安娜女士……", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至今我都銘記在心，最艱難的歲月裡，我和我的船員們是如何幫助他們的！", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#8$1"}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是科魯茲與我帶著自己的船員為他們驅趕前來侵擾的海嗣！", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#8$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我們省出為數不多的糧食，好讓他們不必去啃食同類的屍體！", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#8$1"}, {"id": 438, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他們呢？等審判庭一來，他們又毫不留情將我們趕進鹽漠深處！", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#4$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不是他們見死不救，科魯茲又怎會淪落到那個境地！", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#8$1"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我絕不會向那些忘恩負義的東西低頭……", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#8$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我愛你們所有人，小哈，不論你是否相信，就像我愛當年與我一起在海浪中拚殺的夥伴。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#2$1"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然他們早已逝去，從你們這些孩子的臉上，我還能依稀看到他們的模樣。這讓我不禁感嘆，來自血脈的傳承是多麼神奇的事情。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#8$1"}, {"id": 447, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我無法原諒……請你理解，小哈。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#8$1"}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}